           text: Deployment Failed [[$BUILD_PIPELINE_NAME/$BUILD_JOB_NAME]($ATC_EXTERNAL_URL/teams/main/pipelines/$BUILD_PIPELINE_NAME/jobs/$BUILD_JOB_NAME/builds/$BUILD_NAME)].
